<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA17">
<l>ceṉṟanāṭ cellāta ceṅkaṇmā leṅkaṇmā</l>
<l>leṉṟanā ḷennāḷu nāḷāku – meṉṟu</l>
<l>miṟavāta ventai yiṇaiyaṭikkē yāḷāy</l>
<l>maṟavātu vāḻttukaveṉ vāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Of the days gone by, any day is a day that was not gone by</l>
<l>[before I] said: ‘the red-eyed Māl is our Māl’.</l>
<l>Let my mouth praise, without forgetting, being the servant</l>
<l>to both the feet of our Father who will never die.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
